40|$|Coronagraph {{telescope}} and instrument optics for spatial frequencies within {{and beyond the}} spatial control bandwidth of the wave front control system. Three different wave front control systems are considered: a zero-path difference Michelson interferometer with two <b>deformable</b> <b>mirrors</b> at a pupil image; a sequential pair of <b>deformable</b> <b>mirrors</b> with one placed at a pupil image; and the Visible Nuller spatially-filtered controller. We show that the optical bandwidth limits the useful outer working angle...|$|R
