50|$|AEOS is {{equipped}} with an adaptive optics system, the heart {{of which is a}} 941-actuator <b>deformable</b> <b>mirror</b> that can change its shape to remove the atmosphere's distorting effects. Scientists are expected to get near diffraction-limited images of space objects.|$|E
